# Feature Flags — <%= appName %>

JSON-backed feature flags with runtime toggles.

## Environment

```env
FEATURE_FLAGS_PATH=config/feature-flags.json
```

## Usage

```typescript
import { featureFlags } from './src/platform/feature-flags/index.js';

await featureFlags.load();
if (featureFlags.isEnabled('beta-api')) {
  // beta path
}
```

Default flags are generated in `config/feature-flags.json`.
